#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/onsip.rst:72
msgid ""
"Once the OnSIP credentials have been saved, the user can make calls with "
"Odoo **Phone** by clicking the :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Phone)` icon in "
"the top-right corner of Odoo."
